{
  "stem": "19921.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was announced maybe five days later-- you didn't get anything from the same day-- that Russia was attacked to-- by the-- by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, then it came out new lectures that now, really because of that, we really need that wood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Work harder.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we would be working harder, you will be rewarded for it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this and that, because the country has to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, all those political statements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyway, that's the only time which we heard about the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after that, of course, when the news were good, we knew about it because we were told.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When the news were bad, we didn't know anything what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't know that Russia was occupied so fast in the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was absolutely no knowledge about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody told us anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were in the dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And even-- I don't even know if the Russian people themselves knew, because the newspapers didn't reveal either.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because some people went to town, you know, on that pass.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't bring any news that everything is bad or something like that, because the newspapers wouldn't print it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But as soon as something started to get good, everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was through the bullhorn and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, sometimes they even connected the radio to let the people know how great they're doing, so-- but until that point, there was absolute blackout.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We just didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually-- that eventually-- that-- the eventuality came in 1941 right after the United States and Britain ended the Nonaggression Pact with the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in 1941 after the war started.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
